  "history": "The client has a history of academic underperformance despite being described as intelligent, which has likely contributed to persistent self-doubt and frustration. Their experience of isolation at college and subsequent dropout may have reinforced feelings of loneliness and inadequacy. The mother's high expectations appear to have created ongoing pressure and anxiety about meeting familial standards. Financial difficulties and the need to seek help from parents have intensified feelings of dependency and shame. The client has not yet completed their degree and faces ongoing uncertainty about their future.",
